GoBoss version 0.1a
-------------------

Warning : this is an alpha version, use it at your own risks.

To Install
----------
just type 'make'

Requirement
-----------
GoBoss requires SDL, SDL-devel and GnuGo.

To Play
-------
you must be in the GoBoss directory.
then type './goboss'
This will start a 2 player game, that you can leave with ESCAPE.

type './goboss -help' for more options.
(as fullscreen or playing against the computer)


